Programme objectives 

The contribution aims to provide programme support to Pink's ongoing efforts to ensure protection of human rights of the LGBTQI persons through the following objectives;

Objective 1: To strengthen LGBTQI movement through providing safe space, capacity enhancement and full package of services to LGBTQI people and empowering activists and NGOs for addressing the community demands;

Objective 2: To advance evidence-based communication on human rights and LGBTQI related topics through continuous awareness raising and extending collaboration with supporters, allies, partner organizations and coalitions;

Objective 3: To advocate for legal and policy changes for ensuring  inclusiveness of addressing LGBTQI human rights by using national and international advocacy mechanisms; 

Objective 4: To ensure sustainability of the organization and staff capacity building.
